title: Speak Chinese by Suzanne Brickman
description: Updated from the original with additional content, this book on Mandarin for beginners continues to be a bestselling eBook for learning Chinese both in 2012 and 2013. Achievement of this success is due in part to approach taken to teach others simply and easily how to learn Chinese. With visual aides such as charts and even flashcards for the most essential vocabulary, you'll find that learning Chinese truly is possible!
